      "*": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><p><b><a href=\"/Main_Page\" title=\"Main Page\">Home</a> * <a href=\"/Engines\" title=\"Engines\">Engines</a> * RuyDos</b>\n</p>\n<div class=\"thumb tright\"><div class=\"thumbinner\" style=\"width:302px;\"><a href=\"/File:Gravitational-wave_detector_sensitivities_and_astrophysical_gravitational-wave_sources.png\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/a/af/Gravitational-wave_detector_sensitivities_and_astrophysical_gravitational-wave_sources.png/330px-Gravitational-wave_detector_sensitivities_and_astrophysical_gravitational-wave_sources.png\" width=\"300\" height=\"191\" class=\"thumbimage\" srcset=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/a/af/Gravitational-wave_detector_sensitivities_and_astrophysical_gravitational-wave_sources.png/500px-Gravitational-wave_detector_sensitivities_and_astrophysical_gravitational-wave_sources.png 1.5x, https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/a/af/Gravitational-wave_detector_sensitivities_and_astrophysical_gravitational-wave_sources.png/960px-Gravitational-wave_detector_sensitivities_and_astrophysical_gravitational-wave_sources.png 2x\" /></a>  <div class=\"thumbcaption\"><div class=\"magnify\"><a href=\"/File:Gravitational-wave_detector_sensitivities_and_astrophysical_gravitational-wave_sources.png\" class=\"internal\" title=\"Enlarge\"></a></div><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Pink_noise\">Noise</a> curves <sup id=\"cite_ref-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup></div></div></div> \n<p><b>RuyDos</b>,<br />\nan <a href=\"/UCI\" title=\"UCI\">UCI</a> compliant chess engine by <a href=\"/%C3%81lvaro_Begu%C3%A9\" title=\"Álvaro Begué\">Álvaro Begué</a> and <a href=\"/Jos%C3%A9_Manuel_Mor%C3%A1n\" title=\"José Manuel Morán\">José Manuel Morán</a>, written in <a href=\"/Cpp\" title=\"Cpp\">C++</a>, developed since 2013 <sup id=\"cite_ref-2\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup> and first published as <a href=\"/Category:Open_Source\" title=\"Category:Open Source\">open source</a> under the <a href=\"/Massachusetts_Institute_of_Technology#License\" title=\"Massachusetts Institute of Technology\">MIT License</a> in June 2017 <sup id=\"cite_ref-3\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-3\">&#91;3&#93;</a></sup>.\n</p>\n<div id=\"toc\" class=\"toc\"><div class=\"toctitle\"><h2>Contents</h2></div>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-1\"><a href=\"#Etymology\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Etymology</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-2\"><a href=\"#Features\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Features</span></a>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-3\"><a href=\"#Board_Representation\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2.1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Board Representation</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-4\"><a href=\"#Search\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2.2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Search</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-5\"><a href=\"#Evaluation\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2.3</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Evaluation</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-6\"><a href=\"#Misc\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2.4</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Misc</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-7\"><a href=\"#See_also\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">3</span> <span class=\"toctext\">See also</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-8\"><a href=\"#Forum_Posts\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">4</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Forum Posts</span></a>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-9\"><a href=\"#2013_...\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">4.1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">2013 ...</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-10\"><a href=\"#2017\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">4.2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">2017</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-11\"><a href=\"#2018\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">4.3</span> <span class=\"toctext\">2018</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-12\"><a href=\"#External_Links\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">5</span> <span class=\"toctext\">External Links</span></a>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-13\"><a href=\"#Chess_Engine\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">5.1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Chess Engine</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-14\"><a href=\"#Misc_2\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">5.2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Misc</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-15\"><a href=\"#References\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">6</span> <span class=\"toctext\">References</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Etymology\">Etymology</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=RuyDos&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" title=\"Edit section: Etymology\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<p>The name is the <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Spanish_phonology\">Spanish procounciation</a> of \"Ruy 2\", meaning the second program in the <a href=\"/Ruy_Lopez\" title=\"Ruy Lopez\">Ruy-López</a> saga. It is also a <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Homophone\">homophone</a> of the Spanish word \"<a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://es.wikipedia.org/wiki/Ruido\">ruidos</a>\", which means \"<a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Noise\">noises</a>\".\n</p>\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Features\">Features</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=RuyDos&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" title=\"Edit section: Features\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Board_Representation\"><a href=\"/Board_Representation\" title=\"Board Representation\">Board Representation</a></span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=RuyDos&amp;action=edit&amp;section=3\" title=\"Edit section: Board Representation\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li> <a href=\"/Bitboard_Board-Definition\" title=\"Bitboard Board-Definition\">Bitboard Board-Definition</a> </li>\n<li> <a href=\"/8x8_Board\" title=\"8x8 Board\">8x8 Board</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/Square_Mapping_Considerations\" title=\"Square Mapping Considerations\">Little-Endian Rank, Big-Endian File Mapping (LERBEF)</a> (h1=0, a1=7, a8=63)</li>\n<li> <a href=\"/Magic_Bitboards#Fancy\" title=\"Magic Bitboards\">Fancy Magic Bitboards</a></li></ul>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Search\"><a href=\"/Search\" title=\"Search\">Search</a></span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=RuyDos&amp;action=edit&amp;section=4\" title=\"Edit section: Search\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li> <a href=\"/Iterative_Deepening\" title=\"Iterative Deepening\">Iterative Deepening</a> </li>\n<li> <a href=\"/Principal_Variation_Search\" title=\"Principal Variation Search\">Principal Variation Search</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/Transposition_Table\" title=\"Transposition Table\">Transposition Table</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/Selectivity\" title=\"Selectivity\">Selectivity</a></li></ul>\n<dl><dd> <a href=\"/Null_Move_Pruning\" title=\"Null Move Pruning\">Null Move Pruning</a></dd>\n<dd> <a href=\"/Late_Move_Reductions\" title=\"Late Move Reductions\">Late Move Reductions</a></dd>\n<dd> <a href=\"/Check_Extensions\" title=\"Check Extensions\">Check Extensions</a></dd>\n<dd> <a href=\"/Recapture_Extensions\" title=\"Recapture Extensions\">Recapture Extensions</a></dd></dl>\n<ul><li> <a href=\"/Quiescence_Search\" title=\"Quiescence Search\">Quiescence Search</a></li></ul>\n<dl><dd> <a href=\"/Delta_Pruning\" title=\"Delta Pruning\">Delta Pruning</a></dd>\n<dd> <a href=\"/SEE_-_The_Swap_Algorithm\" title=\"SEE - The Swap Algorithm\">SEE &gt; 0</a></dd></dl>\n<ul><li> <a href=\"/Move_Ordering\" title=\"Move Ordering\">Move Ordering</a></li></ul>\n<dl><dd> <a href=\"/MVV-LVA\" title=\"MVV-LVA\">MVV/LVA</a></dd>\n<dd> <a href=\"/Killer_Heuristic\" title=\"Killer Heuristic\">Killer Heuristic</a></dd>\n<dd> <a href=\"/History_Heuristic\" title=\"History Heuristic\">History Heuristic</a></dd></dl>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Evaluation\"><a href=\"/Evaluation\" title=\"Evaluation\">Evaluation</a></span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=RuyDos&amp;action=edit&amp;section=5\" title=\"Edit section: Evaluation\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li> <a href=\"/Material\" title=\"Material\">Material</a> </li></ul>\n<dl><dd> <a href=\"/Material_Hash_Table\" title=\"Material Hash Table\">Material Hash Table</a></dd>\n<dd> <a href=\"/Tapered_Eval\" title=\"Tapered Eval\">Tapered Eval</a> </dd>\n<dd> <a href=\"/Bishop_Pair\" title=\"Bishop Pair\">Bishop Pair</a></dd></dl>\n<ul><li> <a href=\"/Square_Control\" title=\"Square Control\">Square Control</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/Outposts\" title=\"Outposts\">Outposts</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/Pawn_Structure\" title=\"Pawn Structure\">Pawn Structure</a></li></ul>\n<dl><dd> <a href=\"/Backward_Pawn\" title=\"Backward Pawn\">Backward Pawn</a></dd>\n<dd> <a href=\"/Doubled_Pawn\" title=\"Doubled Pawn\">Doubled Pawn</a></dd>\n<dd> <a href=\"/Isolated_Pawn\" title=\"Isolated Pawn\">Isolated Pawn</a></dd></dl>\n<ul><li> <a href=\"/Passed_Pawn\" title=\"Passed Pawn\">Passed Pawn</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/King_Safety\" title=\"King Safety\">King Safety</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/Mobility\" title=\"Mobility\">Mobility</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/Automated_Tuning\" title=\"Automated Tuning\">Tuned</a> with <a href=\"/RuyTune\" title=\"RuyTune\">RuyTune</a></li></ul>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Misc\">Misc</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=RuyDos&amp;action=edit&amp;section=6\" title=\"Edit section: Misc\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li> <a href=\"/Syzygy_Bases\" title=\"Syzygy Bases\">Syzygy Bases</a> via <a href=\"/Syzygy_Bases#Fathom\" title=\"Syzygy Bases\">Fathom</a></li></ul>\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"See_also\">See also</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=RuyDos&amp;action=edit&amp;section=7\" title=\"Edit section: See also\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<ul><li> <a href=\"/Ruy_Lopez\" title=\"Ruy Lopez\">Ruy Lopez</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/RuyTune\" title=\"RuyTune\">RuyTune</a></li></ul>\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Forum_Posts\">Forum Posts</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=RuyDos&amp;action=edit&amp;section=8\" title=\"Edit section: Forum Posts\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"2013_...\">2013 ...</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=RuyDos&amp;action=edit&amp;section=9\" title=\"Edit section: 2013 ...\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=47268\">Suggestions for a sparring partner</a> by <a href=\"/%C3%81lvaro_Begu%C3%A9\" title=\"Álvaro Begué\">Álvaro Begué</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, February 19, 2013</li></ul>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"2017\">2017</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=RuyDos&amp;action=edit&amp;section=10\" title=\"Edit section: 2017\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=64138\">RuyDos publicly available</a> by <a href=\"/%C3%81lvaro_Begu%C3%A9\" title=\"Álvaro Begué\">Álvaro Begué</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, June 01, 2017</li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=64145\">RuyDos publicly available</a> by <a href=\"/%C3%81lvaro_Begu%C3%A9\" title=\"Álvaro Begué\">Álvaro Begué</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a> (General Topics), June 01, 2017</li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=64356\">Testing endgame strength</a> by <a href=\"/%C3%81lvaro_Begu%C3%A9\" title=\"Álvaro Begué\">Álvaro Begué</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, June 21, 2017&#160;» <a href=\"/Engine_Testing\" title=\"Engine Testing\">Engine Testing</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=64377\">Fathom memory usage</a> by <a href=\"/%C3%81lvaro_Begu%C3%A9\" title=\"Álvaro Begué\">Álvaro Begué</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, June 22, 2017&#160;» <a href=\"/Syzygy_Bases\" title=\"Syzygy Bases\">Syzygy Bases</a> via <a href=\"/Syzygy_Bases#Fathom\" title=\"Syzygy Bases\">Fathom</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=64383\">RuyDos with support for syzygy tablebases</a> by <a href=\"/%C3%81lvaro_Begu%C3%A9\" title=\"Álvaro Begué\">Álvaro Begué</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, June 23, 201